@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 12
  BorderColor #1B4F72
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #E8F8F5
  BorderColor #17A589
}

package "After: Production Generator Docs" {
  rectangle "README\n- Compatibility-first quickstart\n- Direct vs gateway summary\n- Canonical docs links" as readme #D4EFDF

  rectangle "docs/generator-config.md\n- Full config reference\n- Direct + gateway behavior\n- Placeholder/naming/feature details\n- Type mapping and identifier safety\n- Migration runbook\n- CI usage (direct + gateway)\n- Troubleshooting matrix\n- Known limitations" as generatorDoc #D6EAF8

  rectangle "Implementation Truth\n- Config discovery order\n- CLI syntax\n- Provider behavior\n- Artifact emission flags\n- Type mapping + escaping" as impl #E8DAEF

  rectangle "Operator Outcomes\n- Fewer config mistakes\n- Safer migrations\n- Deterministic CI checks\n- Clear unsupported-path expectations" as outcomes #FCF3CF
}

readme --> generatorDoc : links to canonical reference
impl --> generatorDoc : verified against source/tests
generatorDoc --> outcomes : actionable guidance

note right of generatorDoc
Known limitations called out:
- Scylla contract placeholder
- Custom SQL introspection deferred
end note

@enduml
